Are We Being Bad Citizens If We Don't Keep Up With the News?

In your opinion, are we being bad citizens if we don't keep up with the news? Do you think all people have some responsibility to know what is going on in the world? Does engaging with current events actually do anything at all? Why do you think the way you do?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think that everyone has some responsibility to know what is going on in the world, but I do not think that it is a requirement.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: However, I do not think that it is necessary for everyone to be a news junkie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think that it is important to be informed, but I do not think that it is necessary to know every detail of every story.
